WEBVTT

13:40.173 --> 13:41.798
I don't want to die.

13:42.589 --> 13:47.089
If I die like everyone else,
how am I different from them?

13:49.798 --> 13:51.048
I have to live.

13:52.131 --> 13:53.298
Give me an idea.

13:54.006 --> 13:55.506
Only one option, sir.

13:56.881 --> 13:58.089
Memory transfer.

14:00.048 --> 14:07.131
Your memory can be transferred from your body to a
different human and thus extending your conscious.
